{"tid":1372834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新 警方會在短時間內派員推進 呼籲集結人士乘坐西鐵離開元朗區","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:59:22.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de397dfea237b85dc467e9d100968dd9b33d6fd1","tid":1372834,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"警方呼籲元朗集結人士盡快離開<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意： <br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播： <br />\n<br />\n今日（七月二十七日）下午約五時開始，警方在元朗由西向東進行驅散行動，大部分人士已經離去。然而，在元朗西鐵站南邊一帶仍然有少量人士集結。 <br />\n<br />\n警方會在短時間內派員推進，呼籲集結人士盡快向北面、乘坐西鐵離開元朗區。 <br />\n<br />\n警方警告，如果仍然有集結人士拒絕離開，警方會作出拘捕。 <br />\n<br />\n警方重申，有關人士已經干犯香港法例《公安條例》中參與未經批准集結的罪行，最高刑罰是監禁五年。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月27日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間21時51分"},{"pid":"92a98961f5540627c0a0100391f578e898cbb0c2","tid":1372834,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/27/P2019072700934.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F27%2FP2019072700934.htm&d=IcHW%2FfQ2zQNJFdNzTrXWKPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=b3bcf06c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/27/P2019072700934.htm</a>"},{"pid":"be1a625e3d22a8100be66853567098d2bf9af34a","tid":1372834,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18114616eda67cc851f345471c1e5fddb17955df","tid":1372834,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b59db0372165973a7022cc663a7ce21429a50c","tid":1372834,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b5681415decc2b6ac3e721bb047af88d81cbcd","tid":1372834,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fed7e12ce88885ed39db91bd22e3f271230e82c","tid":1372834,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"走都唔好散開走，唔好落單"},{"pid":"d9f6dc5bbef3e57b3a2bbb706937b5bda87ce6ec","tid":1372834,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d308e6c3bcb1946b2b11e1cb3fc6b5a6d344bab","tid":1372834,"uid":242724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:59:22.000Z","msg":"現場人士，互相通知"}]}